{"tid":1991521,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"注意：國歌法通過機會好高，大家留意","createTime":"2020-04-27T12:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T13:41:47.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52df3b7cfc7af9874b3d88dbd64a293dcd0c6d3c","tid":1991521,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"政府趁武漢肺炎下的限聚令<br />\n使市民無法圍堵立法會抗議<br />\nDQ郭榮鏗，令郭榮鏗無法再拉布阻國歌法<br />\n<br />\n即係國歌法硬上好有可能成功"},{"pid":"60f1a262e371ad3df081ac7a44ce94941d8417c3","tid":1991521,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"【國歌法】律師會：應清晰定義侮辱國歌行為 3 年監禁不合比例<br />\n<br />\n立法會《國歌法條例草案》委員會本周五（5月24日）再開會。律師會昨日（21日）去信委員會，再要求草案應清晰定義「嚴肅」、「不尊重」、「（國歌的）尊嚴」等字眼。律師會指，若侮辱國歌的行為將來會被刑事化，公眾有權知道條文的清晰定義。<br />\n<br />\n至於現時條例草案建議，侮辱、篡改或歪曲貶損國歌的行為，最高可被判監禁3年及罰款 5 萬元。律師會認為，3 年監禁的刑罰並不合乎比例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國歌法-律師會-應清晰定義侮辱國歌行為-3-年監禁不合比例/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83-%E6%87%89%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A9%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-3-%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=41366629\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83-%E6%87%89%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A9%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-3-%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%2F&h=1c1b84bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國歌法-律師會-應清晰定義侮辱國歌行為-3-年監禁不合比例/</a>"},{"pid":"a70a452fa6a50ff54d89a250010663597ab96ce3","tid":1991521,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52df3b7cfc7af9874b3d88dbd64a293dcd0c6d3c","tid":1991521,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,